OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FThe travel experts Association of
OL,7,FBritish Travel Agents (ABTA) surveyed
OL,8,Fthe different costs of withdrawing
OL,9,Fcash in popular holiday destinations
OL,10,Fto highlight the potential scale of
OL,11,Ffees for travellers.
OL,13,FThey've warned that not only are
OL,14,Fpeople often better off taking cash
OL,15,Fout before going on holiday to avoid
OL,16,Fexpensive fees, but that some
OL,17,Fdestinations aren't willing to accept
OL,18,Fcard payments at all.
OL,20,FSo who charges what?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
