OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FABTA found that it's common to pay
OL,7,Fbetween five and seven euros (#4-#6)
OL,8,Fper withdrawal in some of the most
OL,9,Fpopular holiday destinations.
OL,11,FATMs have fees commonly ranging from
OL,12,F50 cents to six euros (#0.40-#5).
OL,13,FCards are widely accepted but cash is
OL,14,Fstill the most used form of payment.
OL,15,FThough smaller bars and restaurants
OL,16,Fand less cosmopolitan areas often
OL,17,Fdon't accept cards.
