OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FATM fees in Germany range hugely, from
OL,7,Fzero to seven euros (#0-#6) and over.
OL,8,FCash is king in Germany with many bars
OL,9,Fand restaurants not accepting cards,
OL,10,Fespecially in open air venues such as
OL,11,Fbeer gardens and at Christmas markets.
OL,13,FFrench banks do not charge admin fees,
OL,14,Fhowever private ATMs can incur
OL,15,Fexpensive charges. Card and debit
OL,16,Fpayments are widely accepted.
