OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FWithdrawal fees are uncommon if using
OL,7,Fa bank. Cash payments are still very
OL,8,Fcommon in Portugal but cards are also
OL,9,Fwidely accepted.
OL,11,FNetherlands
OL,13,FMost ATMS offer free withdrawals in
OL,14,Fthe Netherlands, however some
OL,15,Findependent operators charge fees.
OL,16,FBoth cash and cards are widely
OL,17,Faccepted.
