OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FMost ATMs in Canada charge between two
OL,7,Fand five Canadian dollars (#1.13-
OL,8,F#2.82), with independent operators
OL,9,Foften charging even more. Free ATMs
OL,10,Fare rare. Card payments are
OL,11,Fsignificantly more popular than cash
OL,12,Fpayments in Canada.
OL,14,FSo how do you best avoid being stung
OL,15,Fwith these fees?
