OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FWhich? travel journalist Harry Kind
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that just like comparing
OL,8,Fprices for hotel bookings, you should
OL,9,Falso be comparing currency conversions
OL,10,Fand always withdrawing cash locally to
OL,11,Favoid often higher fees at the airport
OL,12,Fand abroad.
OL,14,FWhich? also recommend finding a fee-
OL,15,Ffree debit or credit card, where it
OL,16,Fwon't cost anything to spend or
OL,17,Fwithdraw cash. You can found out more
OL,18,Fon the Which? website.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
