OL,3,CSpending abroad: What are the hidden
OL,4,Cfees and how can you avoid them?
OL,6,FAnd if you find yourself at the till
OL,7,Fbeing asked whether to process your
OL,8,Fpayment in local currency or GBP, both
OL,9,FABTA and Which? recommend always
OL,10,Fpaying in the local currency to save
OL,11,Fon additional exchange rate fees.
